{"tid":979392,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[撐起本地娛圈]#梁凱寧 朱智賢 劉佩玥 湯洛雯 朱茵 賴慰玲 18-19 LIHKG香港甲組女神聯賽第十八輪投選專區","createTime":"2019-01-12T15:59:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-14T13:54:55.000Z","uid":92376,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"afdcdf58a06e4a46d8d03a168108d715416074ac","tid":979392,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T15:59:33.000Z","msg":"以下為即將舉行之賽事<br />\n會員可留意稍後時間發出的比賽專用回覆並以回覆評分功能進行投票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n(唔識點樣用回覆評分功能黎投票既巴打可以參考下面既教學)<br />\n<br />\n由首場12:00am開始,每兩分鐘開賽一場<br />\n<br />\n賴慰玲 : 朱智賢<br />\n陳自瑤 : 譚嘉儀(模)<br />\n張沛樂 : 麥美恩<br />\n吳嘉熙@SG : 蔡思貝<br />\n湯洛雯 : 梁凱寧<br />\n陳潔玲 : 姚子羚<br />\n朱茵 : 劉佩玥<br />\n陳敏 : 梁嘉琪<br />\n王敏奕 : 簡幗儀<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/hiNda68.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FhiNda68.png&h=d4221617&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/s2sfX8L.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fs2sfX8L.png&h=b53ffa65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n甲組第十七輪積分榜<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/Z7Fvhhe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FZ7Fvhhe.png&h=15c6f102&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://i.imgur.com/fg4vwe7.png\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Ffg4vwe7.png&d=CY9p5aGPUbqKbEJsZLRVztr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=b77f6a14\" target=\"_blank\">http://i.imgur.com/fg4vwe7.png</a><br />\n有關主場指定額外得分情況,請參閱主場額外分數增幅表<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c23e34fbcbcbe4eb8b6e6c78b4967d765d98c168","tid":979392,"uid":92376,"like":33,"dislike":122,"score":-89,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T16:00:00.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2018-19 LIHKG香港甲組女神聯賽第十八輪</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">*括號內數字為聯賽排名</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2019-1-13 12am-10pm</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/eOgCnrx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FeOgCnrx.png&h=01944232&s={SIZE}\" />  <img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/ljkod1c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fljkod1c.png&h=59f39773&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">(11)賴慰玲vs朱智賢(2)</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">聯賽賽時為22小時，會員可於本回覆發起後22小時內於以回覆評分功能(前者上箭咀;後者下箭咀)投選心水賽事女神。<br />\n在<span style=\"color: red;\">指定時段外</span>的回覆評分功能投票<span style=\"color: red;\">將不作計算</span>在內，請會員密切留意比賽時間。</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">主場女神票數達到15者會按得票相關情況獲得指定額外分數，會員請踴躍投票支持參賽者。</div>"},{"pid":"27a3c2007d947c10bce98b2060a25b3d8d880f34","tid":979392,"uid":227660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T16:01:58.000Z","msg":"Venus洗唔洗降班？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd4cc4c737e17740a29128e262cf967192a337ec","tid":979392,"uid":92376,"like":109,"dislike":34,"score":75,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T16:02:01.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2019-1-13 12:02am-10:02pm</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/EMA3Mis.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FEMA3Mis.png&h=7217db63&s={SIZE}\" />  <img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/eJ30S1i.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FeJ30S1i.png&h=8e05a35f&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">(3)陳自瑤vs譚嘉儀(模)(10)</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">聯賽賽時為22小時，會員可於本回覆發起後22小時內於以回覆評分功能(前者上箭咀;後者下箭咀)投選心水賽事女神。<br />\n在<span style=\"color: red;\">指定時段外</span>的回覆評分功能投票<span style=\"color: red;\">將不作